        "jsCode": "const source = $('10 Build Escalation Email').item.json;\nconst finalReply = source.detectedIntent === 'missing_video'\n  ? \"Thanks for sending those details 😊 I’ve passed this to our media team and they’ll follow up with you shortly.\"\n  : \"Thanks 😊 I’ve passed your request to our team and someone will get back to you shortly.\";\nreturn [{ json: { ...source, finalReply, emailSent: true } }];"
